origin_prompt.content:
你能够调用以下的API:
{'name': 'FinanceAPI.analyze_liquidity_factors', 'description': 'This function analyzes the impact of various factors on market liquidity.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'marketType', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'The type of financial market, e.g., stocks, bonds, commodities.'}, {'name': 'factors', 'type': 'LIST', 'description': 'A list of factors to analyze, e.g., interestRates, creditRisk, marketVolatility.'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'factorImpact', 'description': 'The analysis of how each factor impacts market liquidity.'}]}
请用以下格式进行回复:
想法: 你这一步的目标
动作: 你要调用的API名称
动作参数: JSON格式的参数输入,全部写在一行
调用工具 FinanceAPI.analyze_liquidity_factors, 它的参数输入如下: 'marketType'是'bonds', 'factors'是['interestRates', 'creditRisk', 'marketVolatility'].
